This Lamborghini yacht is the latest addition to UFC fighter #ConorMcgregor! 
The luxury super sports yacht costs $19 million, has two V12 engines that together produce 4,000 horsepower and has a top speed of 110 KM/H. Only 63 units will be produced worldwide. @1.portofino @montecarlo.marine.official
